Simple vertical scroll game. Featuring a charged particle (Lightning) in his way
through the air.
The particle should grab little water drops suspended into air in order to gain
speed due to the reduced resistivity.
Avoid green leaves that reduce your speed.
Grab other smaller charged particles to gain charge.
Travel the maximum possible distance before you loose your charge.

REQUIRES: python2 &  pygame with image support

AUTHOR: Aner Oscar Lucero
